This repo stores the CaseOnly R code for simulateing and analysing data to evaluate type I error and power of the case-only design to detect interactions.

Please cite the following paper if you use it. 

* The case-only design is a powerful approach to detect interactions but should be used with caution.* Rui Dong, Gao T. Wang, Andrew T. DeWan, Suzanne M. Leal. (submitted)
